            "custom_liquid": "<!-- \nURGENCY BADGE SECTION\n\nThis creates a small badge under your Add To Cart button to create urgency.\nExample text: \"Selling Fast - Limited Units Available\"\n\nYou can change:\n1. The text message\n2. The icon\n3. The colors\n-->\n\n<div class=\"ds-urgency-line\">\n\n  <!-- ICON BEFORE TEXT -->\n  <!-- Change this symbol if you want a different icon (⏰ ⏳ ◔ 🕒 etc.) -->\n  <span class=\"ds-clock\">◔</span>\n\n  <!-- URGENCY MESSAGE -->\n  <!-- Edit this text to say whatever urgency message you want -->\n  <span class=\"ds-urgency-text\">\n    <strong>Selling Fast</strong> - Limited Units Available\n  </span>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n\n/* \nCOLOR GUIDE\n\nTo change the colors update these values:\n\nBackground color → background:\nBorder color → border:\nText color → color:\n\nExample colors:\nLavender → #B497D6\nPink → #F4A6B5\nBlue → #4A90E2\nGreen → #3CB371\n*/\n\n.ds-urgency-line {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  gap: 0.45rem;\n  margin-top: 0.75rem;\n  padding: 0.55rem 0.8rem;\n  font-size: 12px;\n  text-align: center;\n\n  /* Border color */\n  border: 1px solid #7c1b2f;\n\n  border-radius: 12px;\n\n  /* Background color */\n  background: #f6e3e7;\n\n  /* Text color */\n  color: #7c1b2f;\n\n  line-height: 1.2;\n}\n\n/* Icon styling */\n.ds-clock {\n  font-size: 14px;\n  line-height: 1;\n  color: #7c1b2f;\n}\n\n/* Makes \"Selling Fast\" slightly bolder */\n.ds-urgency-text strong {\n  font-weight: 600;\n}\n\n</style>"
