            "heading": "Why you'll love it!",
            "icon": "heart",
            "content": "<p>→ Freeze-dried at peak ripeness: anthocyanins, Vitamin C, and Vitamin K preserved<br/>→ 10x the antioxidant concentration of fresh blueberry per gram<br/>→ 100% single ingredient. No maltodextrin, no added sugar, no bulking agents.<br/>→ Dissolves completely in smoothies, yoghurt, oats, baked goods, and water<br/>→ Vibrant natural purple-blue colour — zero artificial dye<br/>→ Shelf-stable for 12 months. No refrigeration needed.<br/>→ FSSAI licensed | Tested for purity | Vegan. Gluten-free.</p>",
            "page": ""
