        "collapsible_tab_PGVm8w": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How to Use",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>Start simple. Stay consistent.<br/><br/><strong>Morning</strong>: 1 tsp stirred into curd or overnight oats<br/><strong>Anytime</strong>: Blend 1-2 tsp into any smoothie or protein shake<br/><strong>Baking</strong>: Replace 5-8% of flour in muffins or pancakes for a nutrition boost and natural purple colour<br/><strong>Drinks</strong>: Whisk into cold lemonade or warm oat milk — turns a vivid violet<br/><strong>Skincare</strong>: Mix 1 tsp with honey for a 10-minute antioxidant face mask<br/><br/>Serving: 1-2 tsp (3-6g) per day. Safe for daily use.<br/>Store cool and dry. No refrigeration needed after opening.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_96AppR": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Nutritional Information",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>Nutritional Information (Approximate per 100g - Freeze Dried Blueberry Powder)<br/><br/>Energy: ~340 kcal<br/>Carbohydrates: ~85g<br/>Dietary Fibre: ~14g<br/>Total Sugar: ~57g (100% naturally occurring berry sugars - zero added)<br/>Protein: ~4g<br/>Total Fat: ~2g<br/><br/>Key bioactive compounds:<br/>◈ Anthocyanins - primary antioxidant; crosses the blood-brain barrier<br/>◈ Vitamin C - collagen synthesis and immune defence<br/>◈ Vitamin K - bone and cardiovascular health<br/>◈ Manganese - metabolic enzyme activation<br/><br/>Ingredients: Freeze Dried Blueberry. Nothing else.<br/>No maltodextrin. No preservatives. No flow agents.<br/>FSSAI Licensed | Tested for purity | Single ingredient</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_hCBUA3": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "More Green Difference",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>Most berry powders on the market are spray-dried with maltodextrin as a carrier. The majority of what you are buying is filler - not berry.<br/><br/>More Green uses freeze-drying: moisture removed at ultra-low temperatures, preserving the anthocyanins, natural flavour, and colour that heat degrades. The result is pure blueberry, concentrated.<br/><br/>◈ Freeze-dried, not spray-dried: anthocyanins survive the process<br/>◈ Zero maltodextrin, zero anti-caking agents<br/>◈ The vibrant purple colour is proof of anthocyanin retention - cheaper powders are often beige-brown<br/>◈ FSSAI licensed | Clean label from Day 1<br/>◈ Single ingredient. Fully traceable.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
